{"tid":2044953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"京恫嚇武統台 美稱做好萬全準備","createTime":"2020-05-31T12:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T12:32:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"303d0a8e02ceb11740be752970da5f09f30670d4","tid":2044953,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:28:10.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200531/VKG5GKCISOPGUMUW6T5LXPSI2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200531%2FVKG5GKCISOPGUMUW6T5LXPSI2Y%2F&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=a5a6e3bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200531%2FVKG5GKCISOPGUMUW6T5LXPSI2Y%2F&h=3f59580f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200531/VKG5GKCISOPGUMUW6T5LXPSI2Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n京恫嚇武統台 美稱做好萬全準備<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GXUYUZQ5PYD2L3UV335LFVRA3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGXUYUZQ5PYD2L3UV335LFVRA3A.jpg&h=d5a0fab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n栗戰書<br />\n<br />\n北京頻頻高調表示不會放棄武統台灣。官媒《人民日報》昨刊出中共政治局常委、全國人大委員長栗戰書日前出席《反分裂國家法》實施15周年座談會的發言全文，表示堅決反對「台獨」分裂，堅定推進祖國和平統一，當。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將改善台軍防衞能力<br />\n<br />\n栗戰書引述《反分裂國家法》第8條，指「台獨」分裂勢力造成台灣從大陸分裂出去的事實，或者將會導致台灣從大。。。。。。。。。。。裂活動，絕非針對台灣同胞。他又稱，堅持做好「非和平方式」作為應對的準備，目的是維護和推進和平統一的前景和進程。<br />\n<br />\n負責東亞事務的。。。。。。。。。。。。有效擊敗對手，「我們有任何你想得到或想不到的方針，用以應付美國未來在全球面臨的挑戰。至於對台灣的支持能否被看見，我更注重功效」。<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》/美聯社"},{"pid":"a5fd379780b9c51d8385621ebb29c7642bde0450","tid":2044953,"uid":216127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:31:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9e59f3f002f703c4e9ce697c2e7bd1219e95cbd","tid":2044953,"uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:32:55.000Z","msg":"快撚啲打一統大業<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/url]"}]}